title: Tomb of the Silent Witch
story: Long after the Silent Witch's fall the tomb remained deserted. Currently it is overrun with snakes, indifferent to the past of the place. Word is that untold treasures of ancient books and magical artifacts can be found here.

notes.text: An uncanny, made of an unknown material breastplate locked in a  safe.
A notable wooden double door with three keyholes to the north.
A half-eaten body of a warlock, a mysterious, glowing flask close to it.
A crate holds a shield, an unknown potion and some gold.
A barbarian, sleeping in a corner.
A key hidden in a crevice of the floor.
A rotten basket with a key.
